  <trk>
    <name>Petit Bisse and Bisse de la Tsandra in Conthey</name>
    <desc>Charming route along two historic Suones in Conthey. The second one offers an interesting insight into this Valais tradition thanks to information panels. The walk also delights with beautiful views.</desc>
